      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "May Fire Quell Fury",
        "Client": "Fugen the Elder",
        "Description": "Bein\u0027 flexible in any situation\u0027s\r\nthe mark of a true hunter, and\r\nI\u0027ve got just the quest to test ya!\r\nIf you can capture me a Rajang,\r\nyou pass\u2014and ya get yourself\r\na new Petalace too! Now, go\r\nget to it!",
        "Target": "Capture a Rajang",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, time expires,\r\nor capture target slain"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Feu et fureur",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027Ancien",
        "Description": "On reconna\u00EEt les vrais chasseurs\r\n\u00E0 leur capacit\u00E9 \u00E0 g\u00E9rer toutes\r\nles situations. Cette fois,\r\ncapture-moi un Rajang pour\r\nr\u00E9ussir la qu\u00EAte et gagner\r\nun nouveau Florelet. Allez,\r\nau boulot !",
        "Target": "Capturer un Rajang",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9\r\nCible tu\u00E9e"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il fuoco che domina la furia",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027anziano",
        "Description": "I veri cacciatori devono\r\nadattarsi a ogni situazione\r\ne questa missione dimostrer\u00E0\r\nse hai questa abilit\u00E0. Se\r\nriesci a catturare un Rajang,\r\ncompleti la missione e ottieni\r\nun nuovo floretto. Su, vai!",
        "Target": "Cattura un Rajang",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero, tempo scaduto\r\no mostro da catturare ucciso"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Zorn mit Feuer bek\u00E4mpfen",
        "Client": "Fogen der \u00C4lteste",
        "Description": "Wahre J\u00E4ger sind in jeder\r\nSituation flexibel, und genau\r\ndas sollst du bei dieser Quest\r\nbeweisen. Du bestehst, wenn du\r\nmir einen Rajang f\u00E4ngst \u2013 ein\r\nganz besonderes Flollier gibt\u0027s\r\nnoch obendrauf! Auf geht\u0027s!",
        "Target": "Fange einen Rajang.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0, Zeit l\u00E4uft ab\r\noder Fangziel erlegt."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Sofoque el fuego a la furia",
        "Client": "Fugen el anciano",
        "Description": "La capacidad para responder\r\nante cualquier situaci\u00F3n es\r\nse\u00F1a de buen cazador, y tengo\r\nalgo con que medirte. Logra\r\ncapturar un Rajang para ver\r\nde qu\u00E9 eres capaz. Adem\u00E1s,\r\n\u00A1te dar\u00E9 un nuevo petalazo!",
        "Target": "Captura un Rajang",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0, agotas\r\nel tiempo o el objetivo muere."
